text: Sivinskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Polozovoskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 91 as of 2010.ВПН-2010. Численность и размещение населения Пермского края There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 14 km north-east from Polozovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Sivinskoye
